Welcome to Sarajevo;;1997;;R;;Drama,War;;6.8;;Michael Winterbottom;;Stephen Dillane,Woody Harrelson,Marisa Tomei,Emira Nusevic,Kerry Fox,Goran Visnjic,James Nesbitt,Emily Lloyd,Igor Dzambazov,Gordana Gadzic,Juliet Aubrey,Drazen Sivak,Vesna Orel,Davor Janjic,Vladimir Jokanovic,Izudina Brutus,Labina Mitevska,Sanja Buric;;American and British journalists Flynn and Michael Henderson, along with their respective news teams, meet at the beginning of the Bosnian war in Sarajevo. During their reports, the group find an orphanage run by the devoted Mrs. Savic near the frontline. Feeling sympathy, Henderson decides to take one of the children, Emira, illegally back to England.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120490/